{"tid":993863,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［book酒店］上野， 高田馬場， 池袋， 邊度好","createTime":"2019-01-24T08:46:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T12:18:43.000Z","uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"97972ba1cd6fb0ae26857ebd7d128ad4ecc55944","tid":993863,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:46:11.000Z","msg":"點解諗呢3個地方， 因為d酒店唔太貴， 又近車站， 但我對呢3個地方都唔熟手， 只知道多野食<br />\n<br />\n只住過澀谷, 但澀谷越黎越貴， 所以想睇下住邊度平<br />\n<br />\n其實冇乜景點要跑， 暫時只定佐東京迪士尼<br />\n<br />\n除咗上面3個地方， 仲有邊度多野食， 近車站， 又唔太貴<br />\n<br />\n酒店Budget最好 $500~$900, 最好唔超過$1000<br />\n<br />\nBtw, 有冇酒店d早餐好正架<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"091bf3419e7d1a7433bb0943f13d0f92c2bf2178","tid":993863,"uid":7741,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:47:24.000Z","msg":"池袋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"111f3e103d916b81fc49ea8a825ed559543117c9","tid":993863,"uid":68081,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:49:07.000Z","msg":"上野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e722902a50120f198c3de7eba1d0e3348c5d09ec","tid":993863,"uid":13664,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:51:20.000Z","msg":"高田馬場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b13905be947a7650cec9d046a0ef3f97c7a68d0b","tid":993863,"uid":1712,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:54:06.000Z","msg":"頂你樓上一人一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8edf2d690cfab591aa6c988d4b81e9148fcc7ca","tid":993863,"uid":11598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-24T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"高輪Gateway"},{"pid":"df3b9583eeae2fc5ff7ab88a3ba3bbb25ae32b2f","tid":993863,